15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/phone-firms-denying-us-military-requests-security-data-letter-says-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>独家：布林肯希望给继任者卢比奥尽可能的“最强牌”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/blinken-wants-give-successor-rubio-strongest-hand-possible-2024-12-04/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周三表示，他的重点是确保马可·卢比奥在下个月接替他时能够在包括乌克兰在内的重大外交政策问题上取得进展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/blinken-wants-give-successor-rubio-strongest-hand-possible-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>拜登访问安哥拉之际，中国对非洲贫困国家实行免税准入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-duty-free-access-poor-african-states-kicks-biden-tours-angola-2024-12-04/</link><description>一位中国高级外交官表示，就在美国总统乔·拜登访问安哥拉之际，中国对非洲最不发达国家的零关税准入本周开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:19:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-duty-free-access-poor-african-states-kicks-biden-tours-angola-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>据 The Information 报道，苹果在将百度人工智能模型适应中国方面面临障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apple-facing-hurdles-adapting-baidu-ai-models-china-information-reports-2024-12-04/</link><description>据 The Information 周三报道，苹果和百度正在努力为在中国销售的 iPhone 添加人工智能功能，但面临着可能损害这家科技巨头在中国手机销售的障碍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:15:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apple-facing-hurdles-adapting-baidu-ai-models-china-information-reports-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员在通报中国盐台风电信黑客事件后誓言采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-agencies-brief-senators-chinese-salt-typhoon-telecom-hacking-2024-12-04/</link><description>美国政府机构周三为所有参议员举行了一次机密简报会，内容涉及中国所谓的“盐台风”深入美国电信公司并窃取美国通话数据的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-agencies-brief-senators-chinese-salt-typhoon-telecom-hacking-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>川崎重挫山东队亚冠，蔚山幸存</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kawasaki-hand-shandong-asian-champions-league-thrashing-while-ulsan-stay-alive-2024-12-04/</link><description>周三，川崎前锋以4-0大胜山东泰山队，增强了晋级亚冠精英赛淘汰赛的希望，而蔚山高清队则在下半场发起反击，击败了上海申花队。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kawasaki-hand-shandong-asian-champions-league-thrashing-while-ulsan-stay-alive-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康任命高管接任被拘留的中国区负责人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-names-new-international-executive-vp-succeed-leon-wang-2024-12-04/</link><description>阿斯利康周三任命 Iskra Reic 为新任国际执行副总裁 (EVP)，接替 10 月份被中国当局拘留的 Leon Wang。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-names-new-international-executive-vp-succeed-leon-wang-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>通用汽车将对中国业务收取超过50亿美元的费用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-take-more-than-5-billion-charges-china-operations-2024-12-04/</link><description>通用汽车周三告诉股东，将对其在华合资企业记录两项总计超过 50 亿美元的非现金费用，一项与业务重组有关，另一项反映其价值下降。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-take-more-than-5-billion-charges-china-operations-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>尼泊尔与中国签署“一带一路”协议，为项目进展铺平道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-china-sign-deal-belt-road-plan-paving-way-progress-projects-2024-12-04/</link><description>尼泊尔外交部周三表示，七年前签署了初步协议，但此后没有取得任何进展，尼泊尔已与中国签署了“一带一路”框架协议，为项目合作铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:19:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-china-sign-deal-belt-road-plan-paving-way-progress-projects-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：鲍威尔在韩国开球后开球，法国等待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:08:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>拜登在安哥拉会见非洲领导人推进洛比托铁路项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-visits-angolan-port-city-lobito-tout-railway-plans-2024-12-04/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三在安哥拉洛比托港会见非洲领导人，推进一项延长铁路的计划，该铁路可以通过洛比托将刚果和赞比亚的重要矿产输送到西方，并对抗中国在该地区的影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 10:20:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-visits-angolan-port-city-lobito-tout-railway-plans-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾和中国就新的南海对抗提出贸易指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-ships-entered-its-territorial-waters-around-disputed-shoal-2024-12-04/</link><description>周三，中国和菲律宾对围绕南海有争议浅滩发生的海上对抗给出了相互矛盾的说法，这是这两个邻国之间长期争端的最新争端。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 01:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-ships-entered-its-territorial-waters-around-disputed-shoal-2024-12-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>